folder: Lafayette Street & Canal Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Lafayette Street, east side, north from Canal, to, and including Howard Streets. The view shows a traffic tower at said intersection.
September 20, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

folder: Canal Street & Lafayette Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Canal Street, south side west from and including Lafayette Street. This view also shows Lafayette Street, at, adjoining and south of the south west corner of Canal Street.

February 25, 1929.

P.L. Sperr.
